{
  "id": null,
  "uid": "cdbct-workload",
  "title": "cdbct — Geo-Partition Resilience + Multi-Tenant",
  "tags": ["cdbct", "workload", "resilience", "multi-tenant"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "5s",
  "time": { "from": "now-15m", "to": "now" },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 3 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Two stories, one dashboard\n\n**Geo-partition resilience** — filter/group by `target`: `global` (3 replicas, balanced), `east/west/eu` (1 replica each, pinned). Partition a node: `cdbct chaos inject partition 1` → east flatlines, others continue.\n\n**Multi-tenant RLS + Admission Control** — filter/group by `qos`: `critical` (20% of tenants), `regular` (60%), `background` (20%). Under load spike: critical stays flat, background latency climbs. Verify isolation: `cdbct tenant verify`."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Write Rate by Target (writes/s)",
      "description": "Drop in a line = that geo-partition target is unavailable.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "cdbct-prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "sum(rate(cdbct_writes_total{target=\"global\"}[30s]))", "legendFormat": "global" },
        { "expr": "sum(rate(cdbct_writes_total{target=\"east\"}[30s]))",   "legendFormat": "east (node 1)" },
        { "expr": "sum(rate(cdbct_writes_total{target=\"west\"}[30s]))",   "legendFormat": "west (node 2)" },
        { "expr": "sum(rate(cdbct_writes_total{target=\"eu\"}[30s]))",     "legendFormat": "eu   (node 3)" }
      ],
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 3, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "ops", "min": 0 },
        "overrides": [
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "global" },       "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "#73BF69", "mode": "fixed" } }] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "east (node 1)" }, "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "#F2CC0C", "mode": "fixed" } }] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "west (node 2)" }, "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "#5794F2", "mode": "fixed" } }] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "eu   (node 3)" }, "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "#B877D9", "mode": "fixed" } }] }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Write Rate by QoS Tier (writes/s)",
      "description": "Under admission control pressure, background rate drops while critical holds steady.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "cdbct-prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "sum(rate(cdbct_writes_total{qos=\"critical\"}[30s]))",   "legendFormat": "critical" },
        { "expr": "sum(rate(cdbct_writes_total{qos=\"regular\"}[30s]))",    "legendFormat": "regular" },
        { "expr": "sum(rate(cdbct_writes_total{qos=\"background\"}[30s]))", "legendFormat": "background" }
      ],
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 3, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "ops", "min": 0 },
        "overrides": [
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "critical" },   "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "#73BF69", "mode": "fixed" } }] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "regular" },    "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "#5794F2", "mode": "fixed" } }] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "background" }, "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "#FF7383", "mode": "fixed" } }] }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Write Errors by Target (errors/s)",
      "description": "Sustained errors on a target = its geo-partition replica is unavailable.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "cdbct-prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "sum(rate(cdbct_write_errors_total{target=\"global\"}[30s]))", "legendFormat": "global" },
        { "expr": "sum(rate(cdbct_write_errors_total{target=\"east\"}[30s]))",   "legendFormat": "east (node 1)" },
        { "expr": "sum(rate(cdbct_write_errors_total{target=\"west\"}[30s]))",   "legendFormat": "west (node 2)" },
        { "expr": "sum(rate(cdbct_write_errors_total{target=\"eu\"}[30s]))",     "legendFormat": "eu   (node 3)" }
      ],
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 11, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "ops", "min": 0,
          "custom": { "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "area" } },
          "thresholds": { "steps": [ { "color": "transparent", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 0.01 } ] }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Write Latency p99 by QoS Tier",
      "description": "The admission control story: under load, critical stays flat while background climbs.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "cdbct-prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (qos, le) (rate(cdbct_write_duration_seconds_bucket{qos=\"critical\"}[30s])))",   "legendFormat": "critical p99" },
        { "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (qos, le) (rate(cdbct_write_duration_seconds_bucket{qos=\"regular\"}[30s])))",    "legendFormat": "regular p99" },
        { "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (qos, le) (rate(cdbct_write_duration_seconds_bucket{qos=\"background\"}[30s])))", "legendFormat": "background p99" }
      ],
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 11, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "s", "min": 0 },
        "overrides": [
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "critical p99" },   "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "#73BF69", "mode": "fixed" } }] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "regular p99" },    "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "#5794F2", "mode": "fixed" } }] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "background p99" }, "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "#FF7383", "mode": "fixed" } }] }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Write Latency p99 by Target",
      "description": "Latency spike on a target = leaseholder re-election in progress (~10s for global, permanent for pinned partitions).",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "cdbct-prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (target, le) (rate(cdbct_write_duration_seconds_bucket{target=\"global\"}[30s])))", "legendFormat": "global p99" },
        { "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (target, le) (rate(cdbct_write_duration_seconds_bucket{target=\"east\"}[30s])))",   "legendFormat": "east p99" },
        { "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (target, le) (rate(cdbct_write_duration_seconds_bucket{target=\"west\"}[30s])))",   "legendFormat": "west p99" },
        { "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (target, le) (rate(cdbct_write_duration_seconds_bucket{target=\"eu\"}[30s])))",     "legendFormat": "eu p99" }
      ],
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 19, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "s", "min": 0 } }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Write Errors by QoS Tier (errors/s)",
      "description": "Background errors spike first under pressure — admission control is working.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "cdbct-prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "sum(rate(cdbct_write_errors_total{qos=\"critical\"}[30s]))",   "legendFormat": "critical" },
        { "expr": "sum(rate(cdbct_write_errors_total{qos=\"regular\"}[30s]))",    "legendFormat": "regular" },
        { "expr": "sum(rate(cdbct_write_errors_total{qos=\"background\"}[30s]))", "legendFormat": "background" }
      ],
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 19, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ops", "min": 0 } }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Live Nodes",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "cdbct-prometheus" },
      "targets": [{ "expr": "max(liveness_livenodes)", "legendFormat": "" }],
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 27, "w": 3, "h": 4 },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "steps": [
        { "color": "red", "value": 0 }, { "color": "orange", "value": 2 }, { "color": "green", "value": 3 }
      ] } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Unavailable Ranges",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "cdbct-prometheus" },
      "targets": [{ "expr": "sum(ranges_unavailable)", "legendFormat": "" }],
      "gridPos": { "x": 3, "y": 27, "w": 3, "h": 4 },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "steps": [
        { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 }
      ] } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Under-replicated",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "cdbct-prometheus" },
      "targets": [{ "expr": "sum(ranges_underreplicated)", "legendFormat": "" }],
      "gridPos": { "x": 6, "y": 27, "w": 3, "h": 4 },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "background" },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "steps": [
        { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "orange", "value": 1 }
      ] } } }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Tenant Pool",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "cdbct-prometheus" },
      "targets": [{ "expr": "sum(cdbct_tenant_pool_size)", "legendFormat": "" }],
      "gridPos": { "x": 9, "y": 27, "w": 3, "h": 4 },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] } },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short" } }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Range Health Over Time",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "cdbct-prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "sum(ranges_unavailable)",     "legendFormat": "unavailable" },
        { "expr": "sum(ranges_underreplicated)", "legendFormat": "under-replicated" }
      ],
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 27, "w": 12, "h": 4 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "short", "min": 0 },
        "overrides": [
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "unavailable" },      "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "red",    "mode": "fixed" } }] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "under-replicated" }, "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "orange", "mode": "fixed" } }] }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Live Nodes Over Time",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "cdbct-prometheus" },
      "targets": [{ "expr": "max(liveness_livenodes)", "legendFormat": "live nodes" }],
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 31, "w": 12, "h": 5 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "min": 0, "max": 5 } }
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Liveness Heartbeat Latency p99",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "cdbct-prometheus" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (instance, le) (rate(liveness_heartbeatlatency_bucket[1m])))", "legendFormat": "{{instance}}" }
      ],
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 31, "w": 12, "h": 5 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "ns" } }
    }
  ]
}
